This repository contains a barebones WebSocket server and client implementation written in 100% Java. The underlying classes are implemented using the Java ServerSocketChannel and SocketChannel classes, which allows for a non-blocking event-driven model (similar to the WebSocket API for web browsers). Implemented WebSocket protocol versions are: Hixie 75, Hixie 76, Hybi 10, and Hybi 17
